_sText:
Hello. This is my very first map, so please do not send any angry messages to me if you spot some misstakes. I will be very gladfull if you could help me by PM if you spot anything like bugs or glitches.

I have made this map from ground. I did not copy anything from electric large, the original map. 
This is just a kind of remix, but made from scratch.
PM me if you want my steam account.

I'll hope you will enjoy it.


Map encludes:
10 cells with 2 spawns in each, teleports, hidden weapons, a VIP cell with 3 spawns, an isolation, garage and medic.
It also includes a pool, showers, wardrobe, bath and other cool stuff.

Have fun!
